subject: Boats and Boating
Sailboats and Sailing
lead_paragraph: Lucio Boggi and crew Manuele LaPorta of Italy won the second race at the 82nd Bacardi Cup Star Class Regatta on Biscayne Bay, near Miami. Peter Bromby of Bermuda and crew Magnus Liljedahl finished second and had the overall lead after two of six races. biscayne.
